人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2088024\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2088024</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG討論區<br />\n<br />\n邊個話冇人 有圖有真相<br />\n<br />\n港島現場慨況<br />\n<br />\n中環已散開，部分回IFC休息<br />\n金鐘入PP，但勿經天橋，危險<br />\n政總冇人，請勿在地面停留<br />\n灣仔小路可行(建議電車路南側)<br />\n可安全來往金銅兩側，勿走近狗總<br />\n銅記大混亂，時代有戲睇，地面有警嫂<br />\n維園開始不平安，請盡快離開<br />\n天后請街坊化，搭車去其他位<br />\n北角極危險，福建黨衛軍<br />\n大西北請提供白衫佬情報<br />\n<br />\n遊行目標已達，<br />\n留有用之軀，今日未完<br />\n<br />\n建議大家下半場前休息食個飯<br />\n請手足們整裝或回家後再出發<br />\n<br />\n==下半場活動==<br />\n<br />\n十八區和理唱正式啟動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2088513\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2088513</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n歡迎查證、報料、更新、轉載 1930"},{"pid":"f55b0291674cc099fceb47b91937b99c553fecdc","tid":2088831,"uid":80393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T11:38:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90cb8c20c8cbc97435236d851850454897b2da6e","tid":2088831,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T11:38:43.000Z","msg":"1856 有人將印有疑似警員個人資料的單張撒在時代廣場二樓地上，吸引市民駐足觀看。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/photos/pcb.3959534647407053/3959534054073779/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcityusu.cbc%2Fphotos%2Fpcb.3959534647407053%2F3959534054073779%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=oa%2BbSijZO%2BDWYSsAyiffbk6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=8c855b09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cityusu.cbc/photos/pcb.3959534647407053/3959534054073779/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"63628713485f913a83dd701ede8c23b27beec004","tid":2088831,"uid":3076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T11:38:52.000Z","msg":"屋企要人"},{"pid":"9d02b9f04f8a107fe6d17a902054dc8dcd016357","tid":2088831,"uid":51209,"like":0,"di